✨ Futuristic Glowing Digital Profile Card Generator Prompt ✨

Use this prompt in Use ChatGPT or Nano Banana in AI Studio to create a stunning, photorealistic image of a transparent digital card showcasing a social media-style profile, held in a hand.

Prompt Template:

"Create a photorealistic, high-resolution image of a natural-looking hand, with visible fingers gently cupping the back of a glowing, transparent glass card. The card is held slightly angled and tilted, presenting a social media-style profile at a dynamic, eye-level perspective.

Profile Details:

Name: [Enter Name Here]

Handle: [Enter @handle Here]

Bio: [Enter Short Bio or Tagline Here]

Website: [Enter URL Here (optional)]

Join Date: [Enter Month Year Here]

Verified: [Yes/No]

Avatar Style/Source: [Describe Avatar - e.g., "A minimalist, circular line-art male avatar," "A gender-neutral flat design avatar," "A photorealistic portrait of a young professional." - *Optional: If using an image-input capable tool, provide URL here: https://example.com/your-avatar.jpg*]

Design Requirements:

The card itself should appear as a sleek, premium digital identity badge.

The edges glow with a smooth [Specify Gradient - e.g., "magenta-blue gradient", "neon green and purple glow"], with the illumination subtly diffusing into the transparent card, highlighting the text from within.

Ultra-sharp, luminous white text, ensuring maximum contrast and readability, mimicking a modern social media profile layout with a verified badge, minimalist icons (link, calendar), and a clean sans-serif font.

The hand exhibits [Describe Skin Tone - eg., "warm, slightly orange skin tones," "fair skin tones," "darker skin tones"], with realistic reflections and soft shadows cast from the glowing card.

The background is dark, softly blurred, and features very subtle, out-of-focus bokeh lights, creating a cinematic depth of field that emphasizes the glowing card.

Overall style: Futuristic, premium, high contrast, 3D photorealistic product shot, evoking a sleek, high-tech atmosphere."

How to Use:

Simply copy the prompt template above and replace the [bracketed placeholders] with your desired details. For the avatar, describe it in text as accurately as possible. If you are using an image generation tool that supports direct image input for elements like avatars, you would provide the URL in the designated spot (though I, as a text-to-image model, will interpret the text description).
